    "created_at": "2025-06-11T22:08:26Z",
    "updated_at": "2025-06-11T22:08:26Z",
    "body": "I noticed that this might have do with the way the prompt format string is written. There can't be blank spaces before nor after the `$fill`, otherwise it will always try to claim that much space. Making this change solved my problem.\n\nHowever, the author of this issue doesn't have spaces around `$fill`, so that might be a different problem.",
